{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Build your pet shop</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You have quite a large land to build your pet shop. You can build your shop on this land according to your pleasure, build shelters for large dogs, do landscaping and place cute decoration objects to attract the attention of your customers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2824380/extras/8.gif?t=1737382830\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2824380/extras/1.gif?t=1737382830\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Take care of your animals</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Feed the animals and watch them grow. Breeding animals will now be much more enjoyable. While breeding animals that are suitable for breeding, you can also discover new and more valuable species.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2824380/extras/4.gif?t=1737382830\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Many animal species</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In this game, which has a very wide animal catalogue, you will be able to feed, breed and find them a family, exotic fish, reptiles, birds, arthropods, as well as cute cats and dogs.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2824380/extras/2.gif?t=1737382830\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2824380/extras/6.gif?t=1737382830\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Customer satisfaction is important</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Happy customers leave positive reviews and increase the shop's reputation. Your shop reputation increases the number of customers and 